Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在发生各种各样乱七八糟的事情之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家终于对战斗的目的这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像懂了又好像没懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又再增加 令人喘不过气的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办，NERGAL先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘机动战舰’
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍着痛苦所踢起的小石头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若反弹回来也会变成钻芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上到手的梦想不算是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请坚信它一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢从不气馁的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想哭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式骄傲地去面对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去热衷的日子是梦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那些碎片收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能看见 以明天为目标的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOING YOUR DAY'S GROW UP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，你肚子痛吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了，走开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你一个 提起精神的诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼晴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，你做什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又作梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经都是十几年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹的作战 ‘接吻吗?’
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在刷牙洗脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督已经来了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟那家伙合不来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在怀疑 山田少尉的那件事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事不是已经有一位\N提督的部下自首了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也经过军法审判了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下舰长又会不安心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么，再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很突然，不过这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说NERGAL与军方达成了协定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但命令移交的部份 认可我们有拒绝权
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于违反 本舰所有成员意见的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我御统百合香必须 以舰长的身份加以拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是 不愿意做个战争的棋子是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们的命令 不是叫你们去打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要你们避开敌人的耳目 完成救出作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出作战?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有遭到木星的攻击 也要保护尊贵的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这抚子的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不得不达成对吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 目前有2637个郁金香在地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是北极海的 乌查兹拉瓦特斯克岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出被留在岛上的 某国亲善大使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会留在这种地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大使的好奇心旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果调查北极海的气象资料 渔场等等的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蚱蜢袭击的话就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌查兹拉瓦特斯克岛 附近海域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前每天都遭到暴风雪侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是要经过这里就很困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹马的感情也到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来他和新女朋友 也没更进一步发展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再谈情说爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够完成这作战的 除了抚子没别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗? 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我们行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子要前往 乌查兹拉瓦特斯克岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之没我们驾驶员的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以养精蓄锐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以好好的养精蓄锐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你缺乏锻练呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话可不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事问我?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…不，百合香的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你马子吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然问这个干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有心上人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候就决定 托付终身给很棒的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没那个意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御统百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用打的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战是没啥卑鄙之分的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再比一次接近战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将进入白令海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于暴风雪，视界为零
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对地，对敌人来说 也是最糟的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未必是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然无法正确判断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没有会成为障碍的岩礁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以从中央突破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎出力降到最低
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤真像洋娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强尼真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲少女的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装模作样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会这么说表示剑你很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦，小孩子给我闭嘴 明人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离开工作岗位没关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛的附近都被暴风雪遮蔽\N无法通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我很闲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说这次作战 泉一个人就能应付了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，只要敌人不出现的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之舞台设定成 21世纪初左右的高中可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于服装等 照标准设定的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间是为了要纾解乘员\N长期处在宇宙空间的精神压力而设置的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自动测量各自的脑波\N还有其他资料进行精神分析
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样噜，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去只属于我们两个人的校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样，好看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠…你的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时代的裙子好短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道是第一次 面对这种状况?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里设定明人是 和我同一个社团的学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，放轻松放轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么紧张的话 没办法纾解压力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎么不紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌，你是怎么了? 明人学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来设定得稍微成人化一点 是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠跑到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，琉璃你担心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是和明人去虚拟实验室了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸于甜蜜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是约会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得火热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，御统舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在发什么呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战行动中怎么可以这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是太过这样 才会让他跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉娜小姐只是个操舵士 为什么那么嚣张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟她曾是  NERGAL会长的秘书嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难免骄纵成性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位快回各自的岗位上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也随时待命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗? 舰长，态度要严厉点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人… 你真的比较喜欢小惠吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，干嘛把门锁上?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说有事要商量 到底什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人学长，我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于这次绘画比赛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你用我当绘画的模特儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，什么? 原来是这样设定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，突然这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是为了学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不可以，小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为，我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方障碍完全清除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始切换为自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都去吃午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃了，琉璃你也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘晚安’\N我喜欢明人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…明人你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你太软弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明夺走了我的初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，总之你先把这个穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长，你讨厌我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我最喜欢学长了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是…明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也跟小惠在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘自动迎击系统开始’
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，只要你吻我 我会再加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急状况 莫非我们被敌人发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续维持力场后退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁出现安定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到敌人射程外还有十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似敌方机动部队重力反应 多数确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在考虑中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持现状速度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS队准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是根据金属探测 推定的敌方数量和位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必刻意去招呼敌方呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的事就让它过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生要向前看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要追究责任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是离开工作岗位的我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式管理是我的职责 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃难道是在包庇舰长吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再白痴白痴了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先，如果要避开 已经被敌方发现的西侧水道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好从东边的群岛部钻过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低空飞行时触礁的可能性 有百分之七十二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是艰难的状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子十分钟之后出发 \N‘休息中’
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线是往东侧的水路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS队 采取警戒态势待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是舰长跑到哪里去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能一个人悲恸欲绝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，天河…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我没资格说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这么消沈 一点也不像你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长，由于我的疏忽 而连累了所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样又笨又钝的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长你也会讨厌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我一定会更加努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教你一个恢复精神的诀窍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人 你该不会是在同情我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火星的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然说过 只要你吻我，我会再加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你为了我好而没这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那个时候一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解你当时的的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人，你不是我的避风港
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的喜欢我再吻我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为… 这是我最重要的初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行员在紧急待命不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来迟了，非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请报告目前状况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰正在岩礁区域行进畔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能在这种地方耽搁喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点 可别让亲善大使给饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前早就 用光燃料冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香，给我大使的岛的座标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座标参照地图A-l3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他四机掩护抚子及明人机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 所有便宜都让你给占尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对舰长有意思的话 就保护好抚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊，金凤花队形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大使…大使呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，能源都快用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下真的完蛋啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊… 视线太差，根本打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，用这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来的，那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河君呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在路上…会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别丧气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让女人流泪啊，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算彻底利用能源 应该也只能再飞十五秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电波障碍清除 可以使用无线电了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS机体讯号无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯也没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，亲善大使啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会，都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的疏忽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把我回收吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正下方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人机，现在归舰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过提督 亲善大使是指它吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说要你们赌命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去保护军方花大笔预算 用实验器材组合的侦查熊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概没有人会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，明人，我好担心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说，我呀，一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得去向舰长报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了，舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了…不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真的忘记了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有纯粹的情感沉睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容与泪水的数目 就会渐渐增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时想要更像自我地去感受风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不属于其他人的我自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去发掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畅销中的我们的主题歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNING
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺从自我，做你自己，做我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就是男人，女人就是女人的时代已经远去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在索性地问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男人昧，有女人昧的活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家熟知的  Saber Marionette J原作者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将向问题作挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下回，机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人味是危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看哦
